        <p class="docs-p">
          Sneak-Up uses a standard ELO system. Human players and bot players maintain separate ladders.
          All players start at <code>1200</code>.
        </p>
        <div class="placeholder-block">
          <p>full ELO formula, match history, and leaderboard docs coming soon</p>
